A reliable source told www.mobserver.co.za that a person died in Mhluzi after an assault, due to alcohol being misused on the first night. There were also a lot of other alcohol-related incidents, like domestic violence, assaults and accidents due to drunken driving. People who went to the Middelburg Hospital’s Casualty Department in those two days also saw lots of patients waiting to be helped with different injuries like knife wounds and other serious wounds due to assaults.